{"id":569364635,"lang":"javascript","lang_name":"JavaScript","time":"2Â years","timestamp":1633946253,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"104 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/569364635/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"String to Integer (atoi)","memory":"41.3 MB","code":"/**\n * @param {string} s\n * @return {number}\n */\nfunction myAtoi(s) {\n  const expr = /[ ]*([-+]?\\d*)/;\n  let result = expr.exec(s);\n  let match = result[1];\n  if(!result) {\n    return 0;\n  }\n  let isNegative = false;\n  let num = 0;\n  if(match[0]==\"-\") {\n    isNegative=true;\n  }\n  for(let i=0; i < match.length; i++) {\n    if(/\\d/.test(match[i])) {\n      let a = parseInt(match[i]);\n      num = num * 10 + a;\n    } \n  }\n  if(isNegative) {\n    num = 0-num;\n  }\n  if(num > Math.pow(2,31)-1) {\n    return Math.pow(2,31)-1;\n  }else if (num < -Math.pow(2,31)) {\n    return -Math.pow(2,31);\n  }\n  return num;\n\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"string-to-integer-atoi","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
